<br />
Darkness isn't a snare, it's a DoT, with a "Decrease Movement Speed" component to it.  A snare is a mob that "Decrease Movement Speed" and that's it.  A DoT is a spell that does damage over time.  If Darkness is a <span style="font-style: italic">snare</span>, is Cessation of Cor a DoT or a debuff?  What is Insideous Retrogression, are you gonna CC the summoning 1k quadder by nuking it for 500+, with the possibility to crit and/or put it in summoning mode?
<br />

<br />
Do you want to kite the snared mob around all day or just make sure it doesn't beat up the cleric while you pull it off for the chanter to mezz it?
<br />

<br />
You can't even spell ignorant, so don't go there.
<br />

