			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Getting back on topic...
<br />

<br />
In the days of cannipet, root was too overpowered.
<br />
In the days when we chaincasted pets regularly, root was too overpowered.
<br />
In the days when the pet/mob disparity was far less than it is now, root was too overpowered.
<br />

<br />
Those days are gone.  Recent changes to the game make a mage very likely to equip and keep his pets around for as long as possible.  Cannipet is gone.  Mobs wipe pets very quickly today.
<br />

<br />
Root, today, isn't overpowered for a mage.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=502692&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold">Zashir Swiftpaw</span></a> -- Savage Lord
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=171313&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold">Eloina Pyromancer</span></a> -- Arch Mage <span style="font-style: italic">[Retired]</span>
<br />
Torvonnilous</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
